30bf7\">@@body:0040@@</h1><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0041@@</p><ol><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0042@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0043@@</p><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0044@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0045@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0046@@</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0047@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0048@@</p></li></ol><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0049@@</p>",
  "segments": {
    "title": {
      "field": "title",
      "text": "Optimizing metadata for SEO and Social Sharing",
      "hash": "b55dac6b5c45"
    },
    "description": {
      "field": "description",
      "text": "",
      "hash": "e3b0c44298fc"
    },
    "body:0001": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "What is metadata?",
      "hash": "1311bc565a87"
    },
    "body:0002": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Metadata is descriptive information about your platform content that appears in search engines or on social media previews. It includes:",
      "hash": "8e55b0289a4b"
    },
    "body:0003": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The meta title (page headline)",
      "hash": "b9981afd9ed1"
    },
    "body:0004": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The meta description (preview text)",
      "hash": "dad3c8d343e9"
    },
    "body:0005": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "The preview image",
      "hash": "ec699716f006"
    },
    "body:0006": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "These tags are not visible on the platform itself, but they influence how people discover and click on your platform externally. Proper metadata improves:",
      "hash": "0659e3e1ad7e"
    },
    "body:0007": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Your platform’s visibility (SEO)",
      "hash": "e4a90453ee7e"
    },
    "body:0008": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "How trustworthy and clear it looks when shared",
      "hash": "ebe700aaab0f"
    },
    "body:0009": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Engagement and click-through rates",
      "hash": "9b90e1484ed6"
    },
    "body:0010": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "What is default metadata on the platform?",
      "hash": "1c70aaf7e26e"
    },
    "body:0011": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Platform homepage",
      "hash": "2d3f6ce3d674"
    },
    "body:0012": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Title: <i>Citizen engagement platform of [Organization Name] | GoVocal</i>",
      "hash": "c5eea4437a0b"
    },
    "body:0013": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Description: <i>Welcome to the online citizen engagement platform of [Organization Name]. Explore local projects and vote on your favourite ideas. Come participate in the discussions!</i>",
      "hash": "76d0ff403117"
    },
